## Decisions and Action Items

* **BBR (`draft-ietf-ccwg-bbr`):** The precautionary bandwidth probing mechanism is accepted as a mandatory component of BBRv3.
* **SCReAM v2 (`draft-ietf-ccwg-rfc8298bis-screamv2`):** 
  * Explicit rate policing detection will not be added to the draft due to excessive complexity.
  * The RFC 9743 evaluation will be kept as part of the working group materials and presentation slides rather than being published as a separate RFC or extensive appendix.

